{"tid":1678034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】青年被制服仍被兜面噴椒 防暴警阻急救稱︰佢好舒服","createTime":"2019-10-27T12:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T13:38:23.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5729ef2a74f30e25ee89e18650060283a132c9a","tid":1678034,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"網民發起「追究警暴 守護民眾 與記者同行」集會，大批市民響應號召出席活動，其間大批示威者與防暴警對峙，警方突然狂射催淚彈製造混亂。至下午4時許，防暴警突然在太空館外向一名穿黑衫青年噴胡椒噴霧，並將其推跌制服，雙手綁上索帶，青年已無任何反抗，但防暴警仍向已制服的青年面部噴椒。<br />\n<br />\n青年其後被防暴警帶到九龍公園徑搜身，有急救員稱見到青年<span style=\"color: red;\">「成面紅晒，不斷嘔水」</span>，他估計青年腹或胸受傷，<span style=\"color: red;\">但防暴警拒讓急救員靠近施救，並指青年「好舒服」</span>。防暴警其後召來一部聲稱救護車，<span style=\"color: red;\">但急救員指該「救護車」只是一部未改裝的豬籠車</span>，車上有紅藍燈，車身並無任何標記。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191027/60201186?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR0nL4TCpwfQMYtTovhr7g5f3S5Yn9h9VOXooukWPgp7wgt1pUGkEaF1AT4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60201186%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR0nL4TCpwfQMYtTovhr7g5f3S5Yn9h9VOXooukWPgp7wgt1pUGkEaF1AT4&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4W5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=46498831\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191027%2F60201186%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR0nL4TCpwfQMYtTovhr7g5f3S5Yn9h9VOXooukWPgp7wgt1pUGkEaF1AT4&h=040fda65\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191027/60201186?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR0nL4TCpwfQMYtTovhr7g5f3S5Yn9h9VOXooukWPgp7wgt1pUGkEaF1AT4</a>"},{"pid":"555a8c97a1d20d3a1b342e8bf8f38f537914b458","tid":1678034,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:33:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M5lARTEZwy4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM5lARTEZwy4&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4W5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=6d5852ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M5lARTEZwy4</a>"},{"pid":"89e3208ab6afdf4dd977ae8c45a82820742e68fa","tid":1678034,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b51cdbc21437cd43daf96eb617504d0e70323b8","tid":1678034,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273807ad745b8099371319b898de0d9d7c2acb1d","tid":1678034,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d48f93639454a5113d72cd34f7aae0a79b3e6426","tid":1678034,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fd06425338cb848ab9b1256327be167203f503","tid":1678034,"uid":270863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re